   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 3990, recto: (1) I, Daniel, swear (an) oath to (2) Mark, thus: By this place, by (3) its holy power, since (4) I have worked with you, neither in (5) the north nor in the south have I (6) concealed from you the two (7) carats, (8) nor in (9) the trading MH 3990, verso: (1) goods.</ab>
         </div>
